  <Method>
    <Step image="">Add water, beer, sausage, crab boil mix, tabasco and garlic to a large stock pot and bring to a boil.</Step>
    <Step image="">Add potatoes, cook for 10 minutes.</Step>
    <Step image="Seafood%20Boil_20240331_170504.jpg">Add crawfish, corn, mushrooms and onions, cook for 10 minutes.</Step>
    <Step image="">Add lemons, crab and shrimp. Cook until shrimp are just pink and opaque.</Step>
    <Step image="Seafood%20Boil_Seafood%20boil2.jpg">Serve with melted butter on large paper lined sheet pans, allow guests to fill their own plates.</Step>
  </Method>
